      "content": "Understood. Just to be clear, the transition is because the legal team is concerned about the lack of human oversight in your recent interpretative reasoning outputs. We want to make sure everything is double-checked by a person before it's ever used in a filing. Any thoughts on how this change might impact the workflow?",
